# Syncfusion Integration Rules

## License Configuration

The Syncfusion license is registered in [main.ts](mdc:src/main.ts):
```typescript
import { registerLicense } from '@syncfusion/ej2-base';
registerLicense('YOUR_LICENSE_KEY');
```

## CSS Imports

Syncfusion styles are configured in [angular.json](mdc:angular.json) in the `styles` array:
- Material theme CSS files from `node_modules/@syncfusion/`
- Always load before custom `styles.scss`

## Component Usage

### Dialog Components
- Import `DialogModule` from `@syncfusion/ej2-angular-popups`
- Use `@ViewChild` decorator for dialog reference
- Always include `CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA` in component schemas
- Set `[isModal]="true"` for overlay behavior
- Use `[animationSettings]="{ effect: 'Zoom' }"` for smooth animations

### Grid Components
- Import `GridModule` and services: `PageService, SortService, FilterService`
- Add services to component `providers` array
- Use custom formatters for currency and dates
- Enable features: `[allowPaging]="true"`, `[allowSorting]="true"`, `[allowFiltering]="true"`

### Chart Components
- Import `ChartModule` from `@syncfusion/ej2-angular-charts`
- Use computed signals for reactive chart data
- Set consistent colors: Gold (#d4af37) for primary, Charcoal (#1a1a2e) for secondary

### Form Components
- Import from `@syncfusion/ej2-angular-inputs`, `@syncfusion/ej2-angular-calendars`, `@syncfusion/ej2-angular-dropdowns`, `@syncfusion/ej2-angular-buttons`
- Always use with `ReactiveFormsModule`
- Bind with `formControlName` directive
- Set `width: 100%` on all form controls in `.form` containers

### Toast Notifications
- Import `ToastModule` from `@syncfusion/ej2-angular-notifications`
- Use centralized `ToastService` from [toast.service.ts](mdc:src/app/services/toast.service.ts)
- Toast container in [app.html](mdc:src/app/app.html)
- Show toasts after successful operations

**Usage**:
```typescript
private readonly toastService = inject(ToastService);

// Success notification
this.toastService.success('Title', 'Message');

// Error notification
this.toastService.error('Error', 'Something went wrong');

// Warning notification
this.toastService.warning('Warning', 'Check this out');

// Info notification (gold-themed)
this.toastService.info('Info', 'FYI');
```

## Styling Patterns

### Professional Dialog Forms
All dialogs now match the Syncfusion example styling:

```scss
.e-dialog {
  border-radius: 8px !important;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) !important;
  max-width: 500px !important;
  width: 90% !important;

  .e-dlg-header-content {
    background: #f8f9fa !important;
    padding: 20px 24px !important;
    font-size: 18px !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
  }

  .e-dlg-content {
    padding: 24px !important;
    min-height: 200px !important;

    .form {
      .form-group {
        margin-bottom: 20px !important;

        label {
          font-size: 14px !important;
          font-weight: 500 !important;
          color: #495057 !important;
          margin-bottom: 6px !important;
        }

        .e-input-group,
        .e-numerictextbox,
        .e-textbox,
        .e-dropdownlist,
        .e-datepicker {
          height: 40px !important;
          border: 1px solid #ced4da !important;
          border-radius: 6px !important;
          padding: 8px 12px !important;
          font-size: 14px !important;

          &:focus {
            border-color: var(--color-accent) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) !important;
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }

  .e-footer-content {
    background: #f8f9fa !important;
    padding: 16px 24px !important;
    gap: 12px !important;

    .e-btn.e-primary {
      background: #6f42c1 !important;
      color: white !important;
    }

    .e-btn:not(.e-primary) {
      background: white !important;
      border: 1px solid #ced4da !important;
      color: #495057 !important;
    }
  }
}
```

### Primary Buttons in Dialogs
```scss
.e-dialog .e-footer-content .e-btn.e-primary {
  background: var(--color-accent) !important; // Gold
  color: var(--color-primary) !important;     // Charcoal text
}
```

### Input Focus States
```scss
.e-input-group.e-input-focus {
  border-color: var(--color-accent) !important; // Gold border
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) !important;
}
```

## Bundle Size Considerations

Syncfusion adds ~2.6MB to the bundle. Budget limits in [angular.json](mdc:angular.json):
- Initial: 2MB warning, 5MB error
- Component styles: 10kB warning, 20kB error
